12:50.937 --> 12:54.791
I guess I hit a nerve.
He's got more problems than you,

12:54.891 --> 12:56.811
and you poop in your air.

13:00.199 --> 13:02.776
Now I know why Barbie and Ken
are sold separately.

13:02.876 --> 13:04.616
Can I move in with you?

13:07.231 --> 13:10.107
