with Linda in my office,

13:10.207 --> 13:12.066
so I moved in with Veronica.

13:12.166 --> 13:16.746
She and I both appreciate a quiet,
professional work environment.

13:20.554 --> 13:25.254
Sorry, I couldn't get any workone
with that hair screaming at me.

13:25.472 --> 13:28.125
The leak has put Veronica
under a little stress, too.

13:28.225 --> 13:30.194
The next day,
the stress intensified,

13:30.294 --> 13:33.554
and so did Veronica's way
of coping with it.

13:40.801 --> 13:43.092
Still, it's easier
than being with Linda.

13:43.192 --> 13:45.245
Besides, Veronica goes
to a lot of meetings,

13:45.345 --> 13:47.505
so I get the place to myself.

13:47.850 --> 13:49.977
They've decided upstairs
to make me the fall guy

13:50.077 --> 13:52.077
for this whole biocomputer thing...

13:52.177 --> 13:53.984
A project that wasn't even mine.

13:54.084 --> 13:57.208
It just dripped on my floor.
- That's a gun.

13:57.308 --> 13:59.072
Blame the bird
that dropped the turd...

13:59.172 --> 14:01.214
You have a gun.
- Not the hat that got the splat.

14:01.314 --> 14:02.802
That's a basic rule of business.

14:02.902 --> 14:06.882
Don't these people know anything?
- What are you doing?

14:10.421 --> 14:11.681
That always works.

14:12.143 --> 14:13.796
Mother...
- You're a guest.

14:13.896 --> 14:18.356
I can't have you flinching
every time I shoot a gun in here.

14:22.154 --> 14:25.414
So it's not really working out
with Veronica.

14:28.347 --> 14:30.520
Have you been able to plug the leak
in the biocomputer?

14:30.620 --> 14:32.731
Because I need it plugged.
I need it plugged bad.

14:32.831 --> 14:35.626
According to my wife,
I'm not good at reading men, either,

14:35.726 --> 14:37.830
but it sounds like...
- I can't go back to my office

14:37.930 --> 14:40.276
because Linda's work habits
drive me crazy.

14:40.376 --> 14:42.824
